<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وفيها:</span> حج بالناس <span class="c2">« ...... »</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
